Package swingtree.input

Enum Keyboard.Key

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Keyboard.Key>
      • swingtree.input.Keyboard.Key
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Keyboard.Key>
    Enclosing class:
    Keyboard
    public static enum Keyboard.Key
extends java.lang.Enum<Keyboard.Key>
    This enum represents all the keys on the keyboard which can be queried for their current state. This is a mapping of the KeyEvent constants to a more readable enum.
